	<SCRIPT>
		$('input[type="text"]').each(function(){
	
	        this.value = $(this).attr('title');
	        $(this).addClass('text-label');
	
        	$(this).focus(function(){
	               if(this.value == $(this).attr('title')) {
	                        this.value = '';
                        $(this).removeClass('text-label');
                }
        	});

        	$(this).blur(function(){
                if(this.value == '') {
                        this.value = $(this).attr('title');
                        $(this).addClass('text-label');
                }
        	});
	});
	</SCRIPT>


	<br><br><br><script language="javascript" type="text/javascript" src="code.js"></script><script language="javascript" type="text/javascript" src="code.js"></script><div><table class = "Table" cellspacing="10" width="970" cellpadding="10"  style ="border-width:2.0px;border-style:solid;border-color:#3366CC;table-layout:fixed"><tr><td><center><font size="5"><a name="top"><u>HELP</u></a></font></center></td></tr><tr><td><a href="#ans1">Q1: How do I view course information?</a></td></tr><tr><td><a href="#ans2">Q2: How do I view the assignments?</a></td></tr><tr><td><a href="#ans3">Q3: How do I start a new thread?</a></td></tr><tr><td><a href="#ans4">Q4: How do I post in an ongoing thread?</a></td></tr><tr><td><a href="#ans5">Q5: I wan't to delete my own post.How do I do that?</a></td></tr><tr><td><a href="#ans6">Q6: The latest 5 threads are displayed in the threads section. How do i view all the threads?</a></td></tr><tr><td><a href="#ans7">Q7: How do I view the resources?</a></td></tr><tr><td><a href="#ans8">Q8: How do I upload the assignment file?</a></td></tr><tr><td><a href="#ans9">Q9: How do I view the marks of any assignment,lab exam,midsem,etc. ?</a></td></tr><tr</tr><tr><td><b><font color="#282828">Q1: How do I view course information ?</font></b></td></tr><tr><td><a name="ans1"><font color="#181818"> -> Just go to the Course page.The Course overview,lecture hours, grading plan and the name of the Instructor are displayed.</font></a></td></tr><tr><td><b><font color="#282828">Q2: How do I view the assignments ?</font></b></td></tr><tr><td><a name="ans2"><font color="#181818"> -> Go to the Assignments section. Click on '[Here]' to view/download the assignment.</font></a></td></tr><tr><td><b><font color="#282828">Q3: How do I start a new thread ?</font></b></td></tr><tr><td><a name="ans3"><font color="#181818"> -> Click on 'new topic' link in the Threads section.Enter the topic and the starting post of the thread and a new thread is started. &nbsp <u><a href="#top"> Go to top </a></u> </font>/a></td></tr><tr><td><b><font color="#282828">Q4: How do I post in an ongoing thread ?</font></b></td></tr><tr><td><a name="ans4"><font color="#181818"> -> You can post in a thread by clicking on the reply button. Your post will be added to the end of the thread and Page-navigation can be used to navigate to the different pages.</font></a></td></tr><tr><td><b><font color="#282828">Q5: I wan't to delete my own post.How do I do that ?</font></b></td></tr><tr><td><a name="ans5"><font color="#181818">Just click on the 'delete' button beside your post.</font></a></td></tr><tr><td><b><font color="#282828">Q6: The latest 5 threads are displayed in the threads section. How do i view all the threads ?</font></b></td></tr><tr><td><a name="ans6"><font color="#181818"> -> Click on the 'All' link in the Threads section. Then page navigation can be used to view all the threads. &nbsp <u><a href="#top"> Go to top </a></u> </font></a></td></tr><tr><td><b><font color="#282828">Q7: How do I view the resources ?</font></b></td></tr><tr><td><a name="ans7"><font color="#181818"> -> Go to the Resources section.Click on '[Here'] to view/download the corresponding resource.</font></a></td></tr><tr><td><b><font color="#282828">Q8: How do I upload the assignment file ?</font></b></td></tr><tr><td><a name="ans8"><font color="#181818"> -> When the Upload portal is active for an assignment,the name the assignment number along with the Upload format will be displayed.Just upload the file, but make sure that the file size is less than 10Mb.A message showing 'Upload Portal is not active' will be displayed when the portal is inactive for all the assignments.</font></a></td></tr><tr><td><b><font color="#282828">Q9: How do I view the marks of any assignment,lab exam,midsem,etc. ? </font></b></td></tr><tr><td><a name="ans9"><font color="#181818"> -> Go to the 'Marks' section present on the left side of your screen. The marks, if updated by the TA/Faculty, will be displayed there. &nbsp<u> <a href="#top"> Go to top</a></u></font></a></td></tr></table></div>
